thread.title_full: SelectQuote Auto & Home reviewed by Jaclyn

author: Jaclyn
title: Jaclyn
text: Mark from SelectQuote: gave me a rate that was almost $100 cheaper than I had found for myself! As a first time homeowner, he explained all of the coverage to me patiently and in a way I could understand! He also did all of this after normal work hours! I have already recommended that my parents give him a call. GREAT SERVICE!
